Description: Framework for the simulation framework for the simulation of complex breeding programs and compare their economic and genetic impact. The package is also used as the background simulator for our a web-based interface <https://www.mobps.de/>. Associated publication: Pook et al. (2020) <doi:10.1534/g3.120.401193>.
